<Layout title="Daniel's First Birthday">
	<main>
		<h1>Daniel's First Birthday</h1>
		<p>They grow up so fast! It seems like just last week that Daniel was born. Now he's turning one! We're so excited to celebrate with you. Please join us for a fun-filled day of food, friends, and family, and animals!</p>
		
		<h2>When?</h2>
		<p>
			<strong>Date: </strong>
			Saturday, May 30, 2026
			<br/>
			<strong>Time: </strong>
			10:30am - 1:30pm
		</p>
		
		<h2>Where?</h2>
		<address>
			Turtle Back Zoo<br/>
      560 Northfield Ave<br />
      West Orange, NJ 07052
		</address>
		<p style="margin-bottom: 1rem">
			<a href="https://www.turtlebackzoo.com/" target="_blank">
				Visit their Website
			</a>
		</p>
		<p>
			<a 
				href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Essex+County+Turtle+Back+Zoo/@40.7676893,-74.2824864,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m6!3m5!1s0x89c3ab9108f88317:0x7d4c14c9be019b5c!8m2!3d40.7676853!4d-74.2799115!16zL20vMGZiOTMy?hl=en-US&entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDQxMi4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D"
				target="_blank"
			>
				Get Directions
			</a>
		</p>

